_sText:
A simple, colourful gun game map.

Was designed to enter into a mapping competition we are hosting on DTK (not to win as I am also judging it, but for lols).

Can house 40 players and is designed to be a meat grinder map, especially when played on GGDM.

**NOTE:** It is highly recommended that you have a FastDownload server for this map. Unpacked, it exceeds 11MB, but compressed (bz2) it is only 600KB.

Feedback is always welcome! :)
